Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:33.26,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}extended its roots
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:41.12,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}and put out a fruit that was still unripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:45.82,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The fruit that I wish would turn orange soon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.82,0:22:48.90,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}is bathed in your light.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:52.64,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The ideals and dreams just swell{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:55.55,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\fnGill Sans Std ExtraBold Display\b1\c&HBDCACF&}H{\r}ey, feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:59.49,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Today, I tried eating an orange
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.49,0:23:02.74,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}but it was so sour I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:06.21,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I couldn’t leave it behind like I have been
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:08.79,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}so I ate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:14.91,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it… I feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.63,0:23:22.05,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it… I love it.
