Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...loving Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to be with Minorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's just too painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was half asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This all must be very traumatic for you, considering you're such good friends with Aisaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you just had a nightmare, Takasu-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let me remind you that the printout is due tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repeat it again for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we weren't seriously injured, and the rescue team saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Taiga's real mother came to pick her up at the resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you contact her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:03:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher told me that Aisaka isn't doing so great,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she's resting at her parents' place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I couldn't reach her cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favour to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend that you're the one who saved Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Taiga asks about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tell her she was unconscious the whole time and said nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this related to the favour Taiga asked me on New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go out somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's eat some good food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Taiga be the only thing on your{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't the people inside taking a bit too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, I'm not keeping you from cooking dinner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for forcing you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I won't go home until I taste the food here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go home either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents will just ask what I'm going to do with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This career assessment is just so they can decide how to split up the classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Notocchi, you're going into liberal arts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I want to go into liberal arts and become an editor for a music magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then finally become a freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy just to graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll have to work for my dad anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being surprised, but you guys are actually thinking about your futures...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what are you talking about?{Gosh just sounds so shit - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan, you're smart enough that you won't have any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going into sciences, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be easy for you and Master Kitamura to pass the national testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, I still haven't decided if I'm going to college{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, find a seat and sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you checked on her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, of course{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liberal arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kushieda, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What about club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since daytime is shorter in winter they're already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, give me your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'll poke your eyes out if you say coal noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coal noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coal noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coal noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, three ramen please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, good choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another new job, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the hourly wage is pretty nice, so I'll try two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have so many jo{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to open his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open his eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endless Circle of Transmigration!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, please come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would never have guessed that she rejected you if you hadn't told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are such unpredictable creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, how are things going with Maya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still ignoring me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl's feelings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she not back because she's really not feeling well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or is her mother being selfish like her father and not letting her come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stop...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did she realise I heard her say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...loving Ryuuji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Career assessment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put something like "I'll study hard", and you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I make it to a four year college,\Nhow much money do you think it'll cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, don't worry about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, a fermented soybean bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're different from Ya-chan because you're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After receiving a great education,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your great talents will launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to live a great life!{org: fabulous, too synonymous with gg trolling - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, isn't there a saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, gold jewel... something polish...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden stone... shining or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A jewel won't shine if it isn't polished"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it gansu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, it's like you're shining when you study!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I work and make around fifty thousand a month...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working at Inage-san's is just an exception within an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to study if you work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we won't be able to have dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A life like that is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be happy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you always tell me to go to college{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, you're no different from other children, even if you don't have a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an super mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be perfectly happy forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfectly happy forever, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga previously said that she's on good terms with her real mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's probably happy to be around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here too, Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're here for the budget estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'll turn it in later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll be counting on you, new team captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, the new student council president sure is busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New team captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you already the team captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kitamura's student council is really busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they merged the male and the female softball team,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was appointed the new team captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably become as busy as Kitamura-kun, since I'm unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then, why are you getting another job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't that make you busier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard the saying that young people must endure hardship, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that hinder both sides{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working hard because I don't want to hinder anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because it's something that can be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that can be seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Amin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful as usual today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that attitude, Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupidity is contagious, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the child is not here, the father can do anything he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Takasu-kun! I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, class is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan to skip first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must it be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you this a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's left to say after all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ghost in that gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears between those two vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was a heartbroken girl who took her{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing has happened so far, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think ghosts have their own personality too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll only appear in front of people who they want to see and understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've seen a ghost before, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't want to yearn and get caught by something I can't see,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then lose the things I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk too much, I don't want to hear the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand after you've heard the whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to say that if I just watch and don't interfere,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything will turn out fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, talking to you feels like having a period.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hesitate anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will look forward and try to get what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hesitate anymore, I swear! I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is about your career assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I still haven't talked to my family about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you still feel the same as at the beginning of this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:14:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an overachieving student, and I expect a lot from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is why I'm concerned about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how being a teacher is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't have expectations for me, my family is poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the problem is financial?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need it, there are different scholarships and financial aids{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it so strange to not go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I couldn't tell with just this career assessment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's how you feel about it, not how others feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why is it so dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Job?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what she means by, "There's always a way"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she also say it'd be pointless if a mother and son didn't have dinner together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, it's like you're shining when you study!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I give it to her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How is a love letter embarrassing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Disgusting, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I don't have the guts to confess to her, I can only imagine like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's horribly miserable, but I don't think it's embarrassing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, the feeling of liking someone is not embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that to the person who likes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't say it even if I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, she's not answering my calls!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, why are you work{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-T{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you, and who were you with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You nearly killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, pig, dog, yaksha, asura, gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No running!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to strangle me and looked at me with weird eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was just surprised because you appeared out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was really worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the battery died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to explain everything to me in detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you didn't come back because you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wound isn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing about me not doing so great was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see, so you're all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't seen my mum for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stayed at a hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we went shopping, to restaurants, and movies and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just being a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let me in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you weren't going to come over anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go in through the window from your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the three-second rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can you do it within three seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for intruding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't you have dinner here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some fermented beans left, so I'll just add some onions{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I already had dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh yeah, Inko-chan wants to say hi to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's his new greeting! He learned it recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that ugly bird get fatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're not here to stress him{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scratch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's eating too much because he's so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's as ugly as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, being with Taiga is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuj{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just yawning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's late, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, ugly one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just cleaning out stuff because I had time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I didn't have time at the end of last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:08.20,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really clumsy, but I finally understood after what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm clumsy, I can still be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop thinking about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you find out Minorin's true feelings yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you didn't ask her because of the fuss I caused...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she worrying about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:39.44,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I won't be clumsy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things will definitely turn out fine between you and Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji! Don't just stand there, come and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always forget to lock the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A highly secured mansion isn't always convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I nearly forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Kitamura-kun, and Minorin went to look for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my dreams, Kitamura-kun was carrying me on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I muttered something stupid to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:21:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something stupid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she want to pretend she didn't say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun did carry you on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you didn't say anything because you were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I heard, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a second, I was worried that it had been real.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, you're really a...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...klutz, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.43,0:23:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-year-old rock-paper-scissors: scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine's Day is awesome!
